WEBVTT

00:00:01.105 --> 00:00:05.315
[Episode 8: I Just Want to See You]

00:00:12.112 --> 00:00:15.015
Want some black tea?

00:00:15.015 --> 00:00:18.651
If you want bitter gourd,
you can buy it at the market.

00:00:18.651 --> 00:00:20.520
Or do you want to draw a card first

00:00:20.520 --> 00:00:22.510
before deciding whether to drink it?

00:00:27.994 --> 00:00:29.570
Who are you?

00:00:30.897 --> 00:00:32.966
I am...

00:00:32.966 --> 00:00:37.169
a turtle who likes to befriend mermaids.

00:00:41.074 --> 00:00:42.242
Have a seat, mermaid.

00:00:42.242 --> 00:00:44.003
Want some candy?

00:00:49.349 --> 00:00:51.785
You know, there are many
shooting stars here on Starry Islet.

00:00:51.785 --> 00:00:53.463
You can make a wish.

00:01:01.361 --> 00:01:03.496
Making a wish is like a trade.

00:01:03.496 --> 00:01:06.765
When your wish comes true,
something else will...

00:01:09.469 --> 00:01:12.505
I wonder how long the happiness gained

00:01:12.505 --> 00:01:14.517
from making a wish can actually last.

00:01:16.142 --> 00:01:18.143
You're really not having any?

00:01:19.379 --> 00:01:20.947
Fine, forget it then.

00:01:20.947 --> 00:01:23.015
You don't know what's good.

00:02:37.624 --> 00:02:38.725
Thanks for visiting!

00:02:38.725 --> 00:02:40.360
Bye-bye!

00:02:40.360 --> 00:02:41.928
Your place is really wonderful.

00:02:41.928 --> 00:02:42.996
Thank you.

00:02:42.996 --> 00:02:43.830
Get home safely.

00:02:43.830 --> 00:02:45.991
Bye-bye!

00:03:40.253 --> 00:03:42.121
Chen Hao Wei...

00:03:42.121 --> 00:03:44.306
I really miss you.

00:05:24.657 --> 00:05:26.025
He's so handsome!

00:05:26.025 --> 00:05:27.293
I've never seen anyone so handsome.

00:05:27.293 --> 00:05:30.396
Okay, I'll go pay first.

00:05:30.396 --> 00:05:31.432
Can I take a photo with you?

00:05:31.432 --> 00:05:32.464
Sure.

00:05:32.464 --> 00:05:33.833
- So handsome!
- Sure thing.

00:05:33.833 --> 00:05:35.501
Hey, wait for me!

00:05:35.501 --> 00:05:37.570
Thank you.

00:05:37.570 --> 00:05:40.039
Was the food good? Good, okay.

00:05:40.039 --> 00:05:41.107
Here's 30 dollars change.

00:05:41.107 --> 00:05:42.508
- Okay.
- Come back again soon!

00:05:42.508 --> 00:05:44.944
- Thanks, we definitely will!
- Thank you.

00:05:44.944 --> 00:05:46.813
- Thank you!
- I want a photo too!

00:05:46.813 --> 00:05:48.473
Wait for me!

00:05:51.150 --> 00:05:52.151
Mom.

00:05:52.151 --> 00:05:53.619
I'm off the clock.

00:05:53.619 --> 00:05:54.966
Okay.

00:05:57.590 --> 00:05:59.692
All right.

00:05:59.692 --> 00:06:01.394
Her turn.

00:06:01.394 --> 00:06:03.629
Hey, uh, you...

00:06:03.629 --> 00:06:04.897
Li Wan Zhe.

00:06:04.897 --> 00:06:08.000
Didn't you say you wanted to
improve employee benefits?

00:06:09.102 --> 00:06:10.370
For our employee's birthday this year,

00:06:10.370 --> 00:06:12.472
the boss is upping the ante.

00:06:12.472 --> 00:06:14.674
What? Are you giving me a bonus?

00:06:14.674 --> 00:06:15.708
Something like that.

00:06:15.708 --> 00:06:17.410
I'll take the money for your bonus,

00:06:17.410 --> 00:06:18.411
and we'll use it to buy...

00:06:18.411 --> 00:06:20.012
Wagyu beef, how about that?

00:06:20.012 --> 00:06:21.481
Iberico pork.

00:06:21.481 --> 00:06:23.615
I'd rather have cherry duck.

00:06:24.450 --> 00:06:25.918
Food again?

00:06:25.918 --> 00:06:27.820
Hama-chan has already bought
so much good food lately.

00:06:27.820 --> 00:06:29.355
I'm not interested in food.

00:06:29.355 --> 00:06:31.457
I'm fine with eating whatever.

00:06:31.457 --> 00:06:32.992
Are you sure?

00:06:32.992 --> 00:06:34.026
Let me tell you,

00:06:34.026 --> 00:06:37.563
you'll have a "9" in your lunar age next year.

00:06:37.563 --> 00:06:39.365
You can't have a big celebration then.

00:06:39.365 --> 00:06:40.566
So, if you miss this year,

00:06:40.566 --> 00:06:41.934
you'll have to wait two more years.

00:06:41.934 --> 00:06:43.069
I'm sure.

00:06:43.069 --> 00:06:44.237
Anyway, as long as Hama-chan is here,

00:06:44.237 --> 00:06:45.471
I get to eat a feast every day.

00:06:45.471 --> 00:06:47.440
Every day feels like my birthday.

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:49.909
You're too much. I'm a widow.

00:06:49.909 --> 00:06:52.845
Are you flaunting your love
in front of a widow?

00:06:52.845 --> 00:06:53.980
When Dad was still alive,

00:06:53.980 --> 00:06:56.315
didn't you two flaunt it every day too?

00:06:59.118 --> 00:07:01.154
That's true.

00:07:01.154 --> 00:07:03.623
Your dad and I had a long honeymoon.

00:07:03.623 --> 00:07:06.191
It lasted until the day he passed away.

00:07:07.827 --> 00:07:10.963
Wait, I want one, too.

00:07:10.963 --> 00:07:12.832
- Hold on.
- Okay, our turn.

00:07:12.832 --> 00:07:14.333
- Okay.
- Hurry, it's our turn.

00:07:14.333 --> 00:07:16.836
- Hurry and take a photo for us.
- Careful!

00:07:16.836 --> 00:07:18.304
Mom.

00:07:18.304 --> 00:07:19.772
When you and Dad were together,

00:07:19.772 --> 00:07:21.500
who confessed first?

00:07:23.176 --> 00:07:24.444
No way.

00:07:24.444 --> 00:07:26.045
He's already working at our place,

00:07:26.045 --> 00:07:28.347
and you're still not officially dating?

00:07:28.347 --> 00:07:30.183
I just haven't found the right time

00:07:30.183 --> 00:07:31.215
to talk to him about it.

00:07:31.215 --> 00:07:33.386
Besides, I don't know what to say.

00:07:33.386 --> 00:07:35.354
Think? What's there to think about?

00:07:35.354 --> 00:07:36.823
Just do it.

00:07:36.823 --> 00:07:39.157
Do it? Do what?

00:07:39.859 --> 00:07:42.395
Do I really have to teach you?

00:07:42.395 --> 00:07:45.998
Come here. Let me teach you
some tricks on how to be a man.

00:07:45.998 --> 00:07:47.099
Listen to me.

00:07:47.099 --> 00:07:48.267
Good.

00:07:48.267 --> 00:07:50.303
Go on.

00:07:50.303 --> 00:07:53.139
You should get yourself drunk first.

00:07:53.139 --> 00:07:54.973
And then...

00:07:56.876 --> 00:07:57.977
Go on.

00:07:57.977 --> 00:07:59.245
And then you...

00:07:59.245 --> 00:08:01.647
But I have low alcohol tolerance.

00:08:01.647 --> 00:08:03.883
Just go...

00:08:03.883 --> 00:08:05.318
Hama-chan, thanks for your hard work.

00:08:05.318 --> 00:08:06.452
- Thanks for the hard work.
- It's nothing.

00:08:06.452 --> 00:08:09.722
Auntie, I have to be
on the main island tomorrow.

00:08:09.722 --> 00:08:12.024
I'd like to take a day off.

00:08:12.024 --> 00:08:13.626
Tomorrow? It's Wan Zhe's birthday.

00:08:13.626 --> 00:08:15.661
- Aren't you coming?
- I am.

00:08:15.661 --> 00:08:18.196
I'm only taking half a day off.

00:08:20.500 --> 00:08:22.602
I'll make it back, all right?

00:08:22.602 --> 00:08:24.704
On the last ferry.

00:08:24.704 --> 00:08:26.472
Okay.

00:08:26.472 --> 00:08:28.940
I need to scoop out the tapioca balls.

00:08:32.311 --> 00:08:33.817
Hama-chan.

00:08:44.490 --> 00:08:45.892
By the way,

00:08:45.892 --> 00:08:47.026
if you're going to the main island,

00:08:47.026 --> 00:08:49.328
stop by Matsumoto Kiyoshi and buy me

00:08:49.328 --> 00:08:51.931
that Chocola BB Plus from Japan.

00:08:51.931 --> 00:08:53.399
Why?

00:08:53.399 --> 00:08:55.268
Because that's the Vitamin B supplement

00:08:55.268 --> 00:08:56.502
Angela must take every day.

00:08:56.502 --> 00:08:58.704
The small sugar-coated tablets
are easy to swallow and have no weird smell.

00:08:58.704 --> 00:09:00.506
Most importantly, it has no weird smell.

00:09:00.506 --> 00:09:03.009
It provides nutrients and keeps you energetic.

00:09:03.009 --> 00:09:06.245
Otherwise, how can she be
the beauty of Starry Islet?

00:09:06.245 --> 00:09:08.981
Besides, for busy people like us,

00:09:08.981 --> 00:09:11.750
we need the vitality from BB Plus.

00:09:12.485 --> 00:09:16.422
You won't be cute if you're tired.

00:09:16.422 --> 00:09:18.258
Understood.

00:09:18.258 --> 00:09:19.289
Go back to your work.

00:09:19.289 --> 00:09:21.193
- The tapioca will get mushy.
- All right.

00:09:27.233 --> 00:09:29.969
By the way, can you still
make it back tomorrow?

00:09:29.969 --> 00:09:30.970
It's your birthday.

00:09:30.970 --> 00:09:33.339
I'll definitely be there.

00:09:33.339 --> 00:09:35.041
Did I say you had to be there?

00:09:35.041 --> 00:09:37.777
Come or not, it's up to you.

00:09:37.777 --> 00:09:39.412
Don't worry.

00:09:39.412 --> 00:09:42.929
Okay, I got it.

00:09:47.553 --> 00:09:49.088
Li Wan Zhe.

00:09:49.088 --> 00:09:50.890
You're taking this hundred dollars?

00:09:50.890 --> 00:09:52.758
You're becoming such a wimp.

00:09:52.758 --> 00:09:53.759
And you're getting stingier.

00:09:53.759 --> 00:09:55.961
Taking even a hundred dollars.

00:10:00.099 --> 00:10:01.901
Mom, I'm going to help Hama-chan.

00:10:01.901 --> 00:10:03.542
Go ahead.

00:10:31.130 --> 00:10:33.008
I'm giving you two days off.

00:10:34.867 --> 00:10:36.542
What?

00:10:41.140 --> 00:10:42.908
Why is there so much money?

00:10:42.908 --> 00:10:44.210
What's this address?

00:10:44.210 --> 00:10:46.012
You want me to go to the main island?

00:10:46.012 --> 00:10:48.146
Go find Chen Hao Wei.

00:10:50.016 --> 00:10:51.684
Either talk things through with him,

00:10:51.684 --> 00:10:54.619
or just bag him and bring him back.

00:11:00.426 --> 00:11:02.995
Do you think I'm as stupid as you?

00:11:02.995 --> 00:11:04.430
Ever since the day Hao Wei left,

00:11:04.430 --> 00:11:07.233
you've been acting so strange.

00:11:07.233 --> 00:11:09.268
When you saw him off at the pier,

00:11:09.268 --> 00:11:10.302
that face of yours...

00:11:10.302 --> 00:11:14.231
It looked as awful as if
you'd just come from a funeral.

00:11:14.231 --> 00:11:17.404
Moping around like a crazy person every day.

00:11:18.444 --> 00:11:20.279
That's such an exaggeration.

00:11:20.279 --> 00:11:22.515
Don't be so mean.

00:11:22.515 --> 00:11:23.582
No matter how mean I sound,

00:11:23.582 --> 00:11:26.185
it's not as bad as your face, you know?

00:11:26.185 --> 00:11:28.621
Young man, you really need to be careful.

00:11:28.621 --> 00:11:30.589
You'll get sick if you keep this up.

00:11:30.589 --> 00:11:33.432
Don't turn my inn into a haunted house.

00:11:36.862 --> 00:11:38.865
Still laughing?

00:11:41.734 --> 00:11:44.370
It's all Mr. Hua's fault.

00:11:44.370 --> 00:11:46.205
He told me about you and Chen Hao Wei.

00:11:46.205 --> 00:11:49.241
I even scolded him for being a busybody.

00:11:49.241 --> 00:11:52.049
But now, I'm being a busybody, too.

00:11:55.548 --> 00:11:56.716
Anyway, you have the money now.

00:11:56.716 --> 00:11:59.918
You have the address and the ticket.

00:12:02.121 --> 00:12:04.942
Now, let's see if you have the heart
to bring him back.

00:12:11.997 --> 00:12:14.165
He Xiang Yong.

00:12:24.343 --> 00:12:25.745
If he's anything like you,

00:12:25.745 --> 00:12:28.413
I'll kick him to death.

00:12:29.482 --> 00:12:31.584
Dudu, let's go. Time for bed.

00:12:31.584 --> 00:12:33.052
This way! Where are you going?

00:12:33.052 --> 00:12:34.687
Go to sleep. This way.

00:12:34.687 --> 00:12:36.888
Let's go. Time for bed.

00:12:42.495 --> 00:12:45.498
I said everything I could that day.

00:12:45.498 --> 00:12:46.899
What on earth do I have to do

00:12:46.899 --> 00:12:49.011
to make him believe me?

00:12:56.108 --> 00:12:59.110
Hello, how can I help you?

00:12:59.712 --> 00:13:01.914
I'm looking for He Xiang Yong.

00:13:01.914 --> 00:13:02.948
I know he has already resigned.

00:13:02.948 --> 00:13:04.817
But I still wanted to come and ask

00:13:04.817 --> 00:13:07.486
if you have his contact information.

00:13:07.486 --> 00:13:09.155
That might not be very convenient.

00:13:09.155 --> 00:13:11.190
Are you...

00:13:11.190 --> 00:13:12.858
Xi Xi!

00:13:12.858 --> 00:13:14.860
The president will be back soon.

00:13:14.860 --> 00:13:16.695
Please have a seat.

00:13:18.197 --> 00:13:19.865
Xi Xi.

00:13:19.865 --> 00:13:21.634
Do you recognize me?

00:13:21.634 --> 00:13:23.135
Starry Islet.

00:13:23.135 --> 00:13:25.104
You gave me a card before.

00:13:25.104 --> 00:13:27.238
You're pretty late.

00:13:29.975 --> 00:13:31.676
I know her.

00:13:39.552 --> 00:13:41.420
Close your eyes.

00:13:41.420 --> 00:13:42.421
Then count...

00:13:42.421 --> 00:13:44.823
142857.

00:13:47.159 --> 00:13:49.094
What caterpillars?

00:13:50.062 --> 00:13:51.797
Do I?

00:13:51.797 --> 00:13:53.666
Stop laughing.

00:13:53.666 --> 00:13:56.668
Don't worry about how others see Chen Hao Wei.

00:13:57.270 --> 00:13:58.270
Aren't you scared?

00:13:58.270 --> 00:14:00.472
What's there to be afraid of?

00:14:00.472 --> 00:14:01.941
Why are you shivering?

00:14:01.941 --> 00:14:04.476
I'm cold from taking a cold shower.

00:14:08.047 --> 00:14:09.181
Fine.

00:14:09.181 --> 00:14:11.150
I'm just as pathetic as him.

00:14:11.150 --> 00:14:12.885
Just as useless.

00:14:12.885 --> 00:14:14.620
We can't do anything right.

00:14:14.620 --> 00:14:15.621
Xiang Yong.

00:14:15.621 --> 00:14:16.622
Have some candy.

00:14:16.622 --> 00:14:18.923
Your favorite watermelon candy.

00:14:20.659 --> 00:14:22.927
I finally found you.

00:14:23.729 --> 00:14:25.764
I won't let go ever again.

00:14:25.764 --> 00:14:28.534
He Xiang Yong.

00:14:28.534 --> 00:14:29.602
Chen Hao Wei.

00:14:29.602 --> 00:14:31.003
I am him.

00:14:31.003 --> 00:14:32.137
I've liked you since ten years ago.

00:14:32.137 --> 00:14:34.106
The one who loved you was always me.

00:14:34.106 --> 00:14:35.774
You were the star of the school,
while I was an outcast.

00:14:35.774 --> 00:14:37.042
I had the worst grades in school.

00:14:37.042 --> 00:14:38.844
We skipped class together
and got caught by the teacher together.

00:14:38.844 --> 00:14:40.079
You tutored me, and I taught you to draw.

00:14:40.079 --> 00:14:41.614
You said I had the hands of Takehiko Inoue.

00:14:41.614 --> 00:14:43.315
- I gave you the drawing for your birthday.
- Enough! That's enough!

00:14:43.315 --> 00:14:44.650
Let me know when you're back.

00:14:44.650 --> 00:14:47.318
- I'll come find you again.
- Bye.

00:14:48.787 --> 00:14:51.189
I believe after he hears what you said,

00:14:52.191 --> 00:14:54.559
he will definitely forgive you.

00:14:57.263 --> 00:14:59.298
He'll also thank you.

00:14:59.298 --> 00:15:01.000
In his life...

00:15:01.000 --> 00:15:03.368
Although he often failed,

00:15:04.570 --> 00:15:08.139
I think, at least in your heart,

00:15:09.608 --> 00:15:11.610
he's still at the top of the list, right?

00:15:11.610 --> 00:15:14.713
You clearly feel that I'm him, don't you?

00:15:14.713 --> 00:15:16.582
Why don't you believe in yourself?

00:15:16.582 --> 00:15:18.683
Chen Hao Wei.

00:15:27.026 --> 00:15:29.461
Have we met somewhere before?

00:15:29.461 --> 00:15:32.697
Nope, never.

00:15:50.950 --> 00:15:52.589
Chen Hao Wei?

00:15:58.290 --> 00:16:00.158
What a coincidence.

00:16:00.993 --> 00:16:02.927
I just got back, too.

00:16:05.097 --> 00:16:06.765
Well...

00:16:07.933 --> 00:16:11.136
There are some things I want to tell you.

00:16:11.136 --> 00:16:13.472
And I want to give this to you.

00:16:13.472 --> 00:16:15.140
I didn't steal it.

00:16:15.140 --> 00:16:16.175
In a way,

00:16:16.175 --> 00:16:18.777
it really does belong to me.

00:16:19.478 --> 00:16:21.613
I thought...

00:16:21.613 --> 00:16:23.582
I'd let you look at what's inside.

00:16:23.582 --> 00:16:25.483
Maybe these things

00:16:26.085 --> 00:16:29.120
will help you remember something.

00:16:30.022 --> 00:16:32.824
But don't feel pressured.

00:16:35.327 --> 00:16:37.496
I know it's hard to believe,

00:16:37.496 --> 00:16:41.066
but it really happened to me.

00:16:41.066 --> 00:16:42.601
I...

00:16:42.601 --> 00:16:44.903
I made a wish on a shooting star.

00:16:46.438 --> 00:16:48.207
And when I woke up,

00:16:48.207 --> 00:16:50.542
I was no longer myself.

00:16:50.542 --> 00:16:51.577
Because I made a wish...

00:16:51.577 --> 00:16:54.145
that I didn't want to be myself anymore.

00:16:55.080 --> 00:16:57.015
What am I even saying?

00:17:01.854 --> 00:17:03.488
I'm sorry.

00:17:04.923 --> 00:17:07.659
I scared you that day.

00:17:09.561 --> 00:17:14.299
Just think of what I said that day as a joke.

00:17:17.770 --> 00:17:19.404
But...

00:17:20.939 --> 00:17:25.476
what I told you at the harbor
that day was all true.

00:17:26.912 --> 00:17:29.447
My feelings for you are real, too.

00:17:31.817 --> 00:17:34.252
I really like you.

00:17:35.187 --> 00:17:37.155
I really do.

00:17:49.835 --> 00:17:51.129
Hao Wei.

00:18:00.212 --> 00:18:01.946
Why?

00:18:03.949 --> 00:18:06.551
Why didn't I believe in myself?

00:18:07.319 --> 00:18:08.787
Why?

00:18:08.787 --> 00:18:10.656
I should have believed you.

00:18:10.656 --> 00:18:12.523
I should've...

00:18:14.426 --> 00:18:16.661
I'm sorry.

00:18:17.996 --> 00:18:20.398
I should have believed you.

00:18:22.134 --> 00:18:24.068
He Xiang Yong.

00:18:26.338 --> 00:18:29.407
I should have believed you.

00:19:41.513 --> 00:19:43.482
Mr. Hamaguchi?

00:19:43.482 --> 00:19:45.250
- Are you the buyer?
- Hello.

00:19:45.250 --> 00:19:46.385
- Hello.
- You're buying the tickets online?

00:19:46.385 --> 00:19:47.559
Yes.

00:19:50.756 --> 00:19:54.593
Two VIP tickets for Quan Zuo Xun.

00:19:54.593 --> 00:19:55.593
Yes.

00:19:55.593 --> 00:19:56.929
- Is it okay?
- Okay.

00:19:56.929 --> 00:19:58.997
Check the money.

00:20:00.299 --> 00:20:01.733
It's all there. I trust you.

00:20:01.733 --> 00:20:02.834
- Is it okay?
- Yes.

00:20:02.834 --> 00:20:04.802
- Go on, hurry up.
- Thank you.

00:20:11.643 --> 00:20:12.778
Hey.

00:20:12.778 --> 00:20:14.479
Xiao Tian.

00:20:18.784 --> 00:20:21.119
Why do you keep smiling at me?

00:20:23.121 --> 00:20:24.690
Excuse me.

00:20:24.690 --> 00:20:25.824
We'll take care of the rest ourselves.

00:20:25.824 --> 00:20:27.159
Okay, no problem.

00:20:27.159 --> 00:20:29.794
Thank you.

00:20:34.533 --> 00:20:36.434
Eat up.

00:20:39.838 --> 00:20:42.006
I keep smiling...

00:20:43.475 --> 00:20:45.476
because I'm so happy.

00:20:48.880 --> 00:20:50.581
I think...

00:20:51.516 --> 00:20:54.152
the fact that we met again

00:20:54.152 --> 00:20:55.821
wasn't luck.

00:20:55.821 --> 00:20:58.156
It wasn't a coincidence, either.

00:20:58.156 --> 00:21:00.225
It's the result of all the years

00:21:00.225 --> 00:21:02.994
I've spent longing for you.

00:21:04.363 --> 00:21:06.431
This time,

00:21:06.431 --> 00:21:08.734
I won't let things end like they did.

00:21:08.734 --> 00:21:11.102
I'll definitely protect you.

00:21:16.675 --> 00:21:18.242
Chen Hao Wei.

00:21:18.977 --> 00:21:20.912
Close your eyes.

00:21:20.912 --> 00:21:22.547
Okay.

00:21:37.195 --> 00:21:38.930
I don't need you to protect me.

00:21:38.930 --> 00:21:41.566
I'm not that weak anymore.

00:21:42.467 --> 00:21:44.169
From now on,

00:21:44.169 --> 00:21:46.404
we should always be happy.

00:21:47.072 --> 00:21:49.028
Let's not have any more regrets.

00:21:50.509 --> 00:21:52.110
Okay?

00:22:00.085 --> 00:22:02.386
Mr. Hamaguchi.

00:22:03.955 --> 00:22:04.956
Who are you?

00:22:04.956 --> 00:22:05.956
Do you know you have to pay a toll

00:22:05.956 --> 00:22:08.126
to pass through here?

00:22:08.126 --> 00:22:09.828
I've never heard of that.

00:22:09.828 --> 00:22:12.096
What are you doing? Let go!

00:22:12.964 --> 00:22:14.665
Give it back!

00:22:15.267 --> 00:22:17.301
Give me back my ticket!

00:22:20.205 --> 00:22:21.807
Give it back!

00:22:21.807 --> 00:22:23.608
Give it back!

00:22:23.608 --> 00:22:25.343
Stop it!

00:22:26.345 --> 00:22:29.488
Give me back my ticket, you jerk!

00:22:30.849 --> 00:22:32.617
- You idiot!
- Stop it!

00:22:32.617 --> 00:22:35.754
- They're fighting!
- Stop it!

00:22:35.754 --> 00:22:37.384
Stop it!

00:22:37.384 --> 00:22:41.798
[Ladder Steps]

00:22:49.701 --> 00:22:52.103
I hope he makes it.

00:23:00.712 --> 00:23:01.847
Hello?

00:23:01.847 --> 00:23:04.182
- Hey!
- Hey, where are you?

00:23:04.182 --> 00:23:05.584
Hello?

00:23:05.584 --> 00:23:08.153
Didn't you say you'd come tonight?

00:23:08.153 --> 00:23:09.421
Wan Zhe.

00:23:09.421 --> 00:23:11.256
What?

00:23:11.256 --> 00:23:12.290
I'm sorry.

00:23:12.290 --> 00:23:14.126
I can't make it back today.

00:23:14.126 --> 00:23:15.227
Why?

00:23:15.227 --> 00:23:16.928
Didn't you promise to celebrate my birthday?

00:23:16.928 --> 00:23:18.830
Here, give me the phone. I'll talk to him.

00:23:18.830 --> 00:23:20.165
Hurry up! Where on earth are you?

00:23:20.165 --> 00:23:21.732
Give it to me.

00:23:22.768 --> 00:23:23.800
Hello?

00:23:23.800 --> 00:23:25.604
Hello, this is Chishi Police Station.

00:23:25.604 --> 00:23:29.007
Are you a relative of Hamaguchi Aomi?

00:23:29.007 --> 00:23:30.342
He needs to be bailed out.

00:23:30.342 --> 00:23:33.678
- Happy birthday to you.
- Okay, I'll be right there.

00:23:33.678 --> 00:23:34.880
Li Wan Zhe.

00:23:34.880 --> 00:23:37.949
Where are you going, birthday boy?

00:23:37.949 --> 00:23:39.317
Li Wan Zhe.

00:23:39.317 --> 00:23:41.385
Say something!

00:23:42.053 --> 00:23:43.722
You know what?

00:23:43.722 --> 00:23:45.457
I went to see Xi Xi.

00:23:45.457 --> 00:23:47.526
After confirming you're He Xiang Yong,

00:23:47.526 --> 00:23:50.362
I was going to rush to Starry Islet,

00:23:50.362 --> 00:23:52.597
but I ran into you at the port.

00:23:55.100 --> 00:23:56.935
My dad was even more extreme.

00:23:56.935 --> 00:23:59.037
He gave me a stack of thousand-dollar bills

00:23:59.037 --> 00:24:00.972
and two ferry tickets.

00:24:00.972 --> 00:24:02.474
He told me to come to the main island,

00:24:02.474 --> 00:24:05.343
bag you up, and bring you back.

00:24:05.343 --> 00:24:07.912
Mr. He is really hilarious.

00:24:11.349 --> 00:24:13.443
What time is it?

00:24:17.088 --> 00:24:18.590
The last ferry is at eleven.

00:24:18.590 --> 00:24:19.624
Hold this.

00:24:19.624 --> 00:24:20.892
I'll go buy your ticket.

00:24:20.892 --> 00:24:22.460
Chen Hao Wei.

00:24:25.230 --> 00:24:27.399
I haven't been to the main island in a while.

00:24:27.399 --> 00:24:29.835
I want to walk around a bit more.

00:24:29.835 --> 00:24:32.670
Wait, then how are you going to get back?

00:24:33.672 --> 00:24:36.208
Do you want me to leave that badly?

00:24:36.208 --> 00:24:38.075
Don't you want to walk with me?

00:24:40.445 --> 00:24:42.914
- That's not what I meant.
- I'm just teasing you.

00:24:42.914 --> 00:24:44.849
Let's go buy the tickets.

00:24:55.594 --> 00:24:58.629
If we're going to walk together,
let's stay with each other for a lifetime.

00:28:47.926 --> 00:28:50.228
Um, I am...

00:28:50.228 --> 00:28:52.129
He's my friend.

00:28:53.732 --> 00:28:54.966
What on earth happened?

00:28:54.966 --> 00:28:56.234
Why did you get into a fight?

00:28:56.234 --> 00:28:58.002
Sir, please don't get worked up.

00:28:58.002 --> 00:28:59.003
Well...

00:28:59.003 --> 00:29:00.405
He's Japanese,

00:29:00.405 --> 00:29:02.707
so his Chinese might not be very fluent.

00:29:02.707 --> 00:29:05.176
What exactly happened? Tell the police.

00:29:05.176 --> 00:29:07.512
Who started it?

00:29:07.512 --> 00:29:09.781
I did.

00:29:09.781 --> 00:29:12.250
Where's the guy he fought with?

00:29:12.250 --> 00:29:13.985
We're checking the CCTV
to understand the situation.

00:29:13.985 --> 00:29:17.088
I need to confirm your identity first.

00:29:17.088 --> 00:29:18.689
Over here.

00:29:21.192 --> 00:29:23.193
Thank you.

00:29:30.201 --> 00:29:31.803
What the hell is going on?

00:29:31.803 --> 00:29:33.605
Do you know it's my birthday today?

00:29:33.605 --> 00:29:35.706
You promised to celebrate it with me.

00:29:37.075 --> 00:29:39.176
Happy birthday.

00:29:40.879 --> 00:29:42.447
What's this?

00:29:42.447 --> 00:29:45.015
Didn't you want to see his concert?

00:29:45.784 --> 00:29:47.980
So, you came to the main island just for this?

00:29:49.420 --> 00:29:51.689
And you got into a fight for this too?

00:29:52.423 --> 00:29:54.626
Because he tried to steal my tickets.

00:29:54.626 --> 00:29:56.827
So, I was going to beat him to death.

00:30:00.632 --> 00:30:02.567
Are you an idiot?

00:30:02.567 --> 00:30:05.023
Am I really worth all this effort?

00:30:07.372 --> 00:30:09.207
What is wrong with you?

00:30:09.207 --> 00:30:10.542
If they had a knife, you'd be dead.

00:30:10.542 --> 00:30:12.911
Do you realize that?

00:30:12.911 --> 00:30:13.945
Li Wan Zhe.

00:30:13.945 --> 00:30:15.779
What?

00:30:16.981 --> 00:30:19.483
If I die like this,

00:30:20.285 --> 00:30:22.553
you'll remember me for the rest of your life.

00:31:02.462 --> 00:31:08.218
[Home is He-re]

00:31:56.381 --> 00:31:57.815
Chen Hao Wei.

00:31:57.815 --> 00:31:58.816
Chen Hao Wei.

00:31:58.816 --> 00:32:00.818
Wake up. Come on.

00:32:00.818 --> 00:32:02.020
How did we get back yesterday?

00:32:02.020 --> 00:32:03.354
- What are you talking about?
- Wake up.

00:32:03.354 --> 00:32:04.789
Look at me.

00:32:04.789 --> 00:32:05.790
Are you messing with me?

00:32:05.790 --> 00:32:08.594
- Are you messing with me?
- You're the one messing with me.

00:32:08.594 --> 00:32:09.526
What are you saying?

00:32:09.526 --> 00:32:12.130
Zhong Xiao You, let me sleep a bit more.

00:32:12.130 --> 00:32:14.331
Why did you call me Zhong Xiao You?

00:32:15.437 --> 00:32:23.403
[Epilogue]

00:32:28.846 --> 00:32:30.581
Do you recognize me?

00:32:30.581 --> 00:32:32.016
Starry Islet.

00:32:32.016 --> 00:32:34.152
You gave me a card before.

00:32:34.152 --> 00:32:36.220
You're pretty late.

00:32:38.122 --> 00:32:40.758
Did you already know that

00:32:40.758 --> 00:32:43.994
I wouldn't understand your hints?

00:32:45.730 --> 00:32:48.800
The end of science is metaphysics.

00:32:48.800 --> 00:32:51.069
Your soul's memory already gave you the answer.

00:32:51.069 --> 00:32:52.071
But you didn't believe it.

00:32:52.071 --> 00:32:53.071
Right?

00:32:53.071 --> 00:32:55.506
Does the name Zhong Xiao You sound familiar?

00:32:55.506 --> 00:32:59.210
Sometimes, I feel like he is He Xiang Yong.

00:32:59.210 --> 00:33:01.145
Frenzied and panicked emotions,

00:33:01.145 --> 00:33:03.247
like a falling meteor.

00:33:03.247 --> 00:33:06.383
So, he really is He Xiang Yong.

00:33:07.251 --> 00:33:10.454
I wonder how long the happiness gained

00:33:11.155 --> 00:33:13.557
from making a wish can actually last.

00:33:15.429 --> 00:33:17.324
I might've revealed too much.

00:33:44.689 --> 00:33:46.958
The wish is starting to backfire.

00:33:46.958 --> 00:33:49.427
Time and space are starting to warp.

00:33:49.427 --> 00:33:50.795
You were married?

00:33:50.795 --> 00:33:53.197
If I were married,
you'd be the Eddie Peng of Starry Islet.

00:33:53.197 --> 00:33:54.632
- Hama-chan.
- What?

00:33:54.632 --> 00:33:56.434
- Where's your injury?
- What injury?

00:33:56.434 --> 00:33:58.870
Does this have to do with
wishing on a shooting star?

00:33:58.870 --> 00:34:00.171
How did you know I made a wish?

00:34:00.171 --> 00:34:01.906
One day, the sea will bring you

00:34:01.906 --> 00:34:04.451
the message it wants to tell you.